OL,3,CGovernment considers welfare reform
OL,4,Cconcessions as Labour MPs threaten to
OL,5,Crevolt
OL,7,FDozens of MPs say that they are
OL,8,Fprepared to vote against the
OL,9,FGovernment's welfare proposals, as ITV
OL,10,FNews Deputy Political Editor Anushka
OL,11,FAsthana explains
OL,13,FSenior Government figures have
OL,14,Faccepted that there will need to be
OL,15,Fconcessions if they are to win a
OL,16,Fparliamentary vote on controversial
OL,17,Fwelfare reforms, ITV News understands.
