OL,3,CGovernment considers welfare reform
OL,4,Cconcessions as Labour MPs threaten to
OL,5,Crevolt
OL,7,FMinisters and officials are weighing
OL,8,Fup what they can offer amid huge anger
OL,9,Facross the parliamentary party, with
OL,10,Fdozens of MPs making clear that they
OL,11,Fare prepared to vote against the
OL,12,Fchanges.
OL,14,FAt least two letters have circulated
OL,15,Famong Labour backbenchers and
OL,16,Fministers, with one attracting almost
OL,17,F120 signatories, and both demanding
OL,18,Fchanges.
