OL,7,FOne that leaked to my colleague,
OL,8,FKieron Clarke at ITV's Good Morning
OL,9,FBritain, wants a consultation on parts
OL,10,Fof the reform to be extended to
OL,11,Finclude the decision to tighten
OL,12,Feligibility for Personal Independence
OL,13,FPayments (PIP), and an impact
OL,14,Fassessment to be carried out and made
OL,15,Favailable to MPs before any vote.
