OL,3,CGovernment considers welfare reform
OL,4,Cconcessions as Labour MPs threaten to
OL,5,Crevolt
OL,7,FSenior whips and government officials
OL,8,Fhave made clear to ITV News that they
OL,9,Fare in "listening" mode as the scale
OL,10,Fof the anger blew up in the wake of
OL,11,Fthe local elections, in which Reform
OL,12,FUK made huge gains, and Labour fell
OL,13,Fback.
OL,15,F"It's a problem," one senior figure
OL,16,Fsaid.
OL,18,F"We are talking large numbers (likely
OL,19,Fto rebel). We need to bring something
OL,20,Fforward if we are to win."
